{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_Njk1Mw_0032","text":"如果生活狠狠的將一切理想 破滅了","structure":{"line_index":32,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["生活","理想","破滅"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["生活","理想","破滅"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,9,3,2,9,9,3,3,3,4,5,9,4,2,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyu4","gwo2","sang1","wut6","han2","han2","dik1","zoeng1","jat1","cai3","lei5","soeng2","po3","mit6","liu5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"如果","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"生活","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"狠狠","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"將","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"一切","pos":"DET"},{"text":"理想","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"破滅","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"}],"syntax_notes":"這句使用假設語氣，描寫生活將理想殘酷摧毀的場景，語氣沉重。"},"source":{"title":"給兒子的信","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6953","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_Njk1Mw_0031","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_Njk1Mw_0033","paragraph_id":"para_08"}}
{"id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_Njk1Mw_0033","text":"還是流我的血 你別忘掉","structure":{"line_index":33,"char_count":10},"semantics":{"themes":["傳承","犧牲","父愛"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["流血","別忘掉"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,0,5,3,4,5,2,0,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["waan4","si6","lau4","ngo5","dik1","hyut3","nei5","bit6","mong4","diu6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"還是","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"流","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"的","pos":"PART"},{"text":"血","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"你別","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"忘掉","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"這句以強烈的意象（流血）表達父親的付出與傳承，語氣懇切。"},"source":{"title":"給兒子的信","artists":["陳奕迅"],"lyricists":["陳詠謙"],"year":0,"genre":["Pop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_6953","prev_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_Njk1Mw_0032","next_line_id":"lyr_6ZmI5aWV6L-F_Njk1Mw_0034","paragraph_id":"para_08"}}
